WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.110
Good morning, family! I'm excited to

00:00:02.120 --> 00:00:04.510
be with you all again today. I have a

00:00:04.520 --> 00:00:07.030
word, and I was praying about

00:00:07.040 --> 00:00:08.390
what I should talk about today.

00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:09.910
Asking the Father, I said, 'Which way do

00:00:09.920 --> 00:00:11.950
you want me to go? Which

00:00:11.960 --> 00:00:16.189
direction?'I

00:00:16.199 --> 00:00:18.470
can go a whole bunch of

00:00:18.480 --> 00:00:20.790
different directions, but in this

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:23.269
case, I feel the Lord is wanting this for

00:00:23.279 --> 00:00:25.790
somebody; it's important for

00:00:25.790 --> 00:00:25.800
someone.

00:00:25.800 --> 00:00:29.070
Being an intercessor and a prayer

00:00:29.080 --> 00:00:31.310
person, I pray a lot. I pray, and the

00:00:31.320 --> 00:00:33.709
Lord will reveal and

00:00:33.709 --> 00:00:33.719
download

00:00:33.719 --> 00:00:36.030
things to me all the time.

00:00:36.040 --> 00:00:38.069
People say, 'How do I get there?'It's

00:00:38.069 --> 00:00:38.079
day-to-day.

00:00:38.079 --> 00:00:42.110
You do it like

00:00:42.120 --> 00:00:44.270
anything

00:00:44.270 --> 00:00:44.280
else—you're

00:00:44.280 --> 00:00:46.029
going to keep going at it.

00:00:46.039 --> 00:00:48.670
You pray, you fast, you

00:00:48.680 --> 00:00:51.229
read your Bible, and you seek His face.

00:00:51.239 --> 00:00:53.709
Whenever you seek Him, the Bible says

00:00:53.719 --> 00:00:55.990
you'll find Him. If you knock, the door

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:58.270
will be opened. I'm telling you, He's respecter

00:00:58.270 --> 00:00:58.280
of

00:00:58.280 --> 00:01:00.310
persons, and what He'll do for

00:01:00.320 --> 00:01:02.790
one, He'll do for another.

00:01:05.239 --> 00:01:07.789
I had been dealing with a lot of

00:01:07.799 --> 00:01:10.830
satanic attacks from this YouTube

00:01:10.840 --> 00:01:13.550
channel.

00:01:13.560 --> 00:01:14.990
He's trying to stop it; he

00:01:14.990 --> 00:01:15.000
doesn't

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:16.550
want me doing this.

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:17.710
With all kinds of stuff from the

00:01:17.720 --> 00:01:21.429
occult,

00:01:21.439 --> 00:01:23.030
you can just feel it in the atmosphere. When you get sensitive to things and

00:01:23.030 --> 00:01:23.040
start maturing with the Lord, you're able to identify atmospheres,

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:24.590
what's going on

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:36.469
in

00:01:36.479 --> 00:01:38.710
the spirit realm for that day,

00:01:38.720 --> 00:01:40.350
and what's coming against you.

00:01:44.399 --> 00:01:48.030
I try not to reveal

00:01:48.040 --> 00:01:50.389
too much because they're a bunch of

00:01:50.399 --> 00:01:51.990
chickens and losers;

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:54.230
we don't give the devil any credit,

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:56.029
but there are things we

00:01:56.039 --> 00:01:57.789
need to talk about so that people know

00:01:57.799 --> 00:01:59.069
how to combat it. The church

00:01:59.069 --> 00:01:59.079
doesn't

00:01:59.079 --> 00:02:00.550
talk about it because they're

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:03.709
a bunch of sugar-coated

00:02:03.719 --> 00:02:05.510
Frosted Flakes. They give you

00:02:05.520 --> 00:02:07.190
just enough to keep you alive,

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:09.869
but it's not making you strong

00:02:09.869 --> 00:02:09.879
or

00:02:09.879 --> 00:02:11.550
able to

00:02:11.550 --> 00:02:11.560
eat

00:02:11.560 --> 00:02:13.030
the meat and know how to fight

00:02:13.040 --> 00:02:15.030
the devil off and be

00:02:15.040 --> 00:02:17.750
victorious in your Christian life.

00:02:17.760 --> 00:02:19.390
They give you the bread of affliction, just enough

00:02:23.440 --> 00:02:25.869
to

00:02:25.879 --> 00:02:28.350
crawl spiritually.

00:02:28.350 --> 00:02:28.360
Pastors,

00:02:28.360 --> 00:02:30.270
shame on you for not teaching

00:02:30.280 --> 00:02:31.949
people how to live by faith, how to

00:02:31.959 --> 00:02:34.309
stand on the Word, and how

00:02:34.309 --> 00:02:34.319
to

00:02:34.319 --> 00:02:37.790
win victoriously.

00:02:42.319 --> 00:02:45.309
I

00:02:45.319 --> 00:02:47.110
had been dealing with that

00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:48.670
occultic stuff and

00:02:48.680 --> 00:02:49.990
was

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:52.149
praying and

00:02:52.159 --> 00:02:55.110
seeking Him, pushing

00:02:55.120 --> 00:02:57.390
back stuff.

00:02:57.400 --> 00:03:00.350
I was asking questions about what

00:03:00.350 --> 00:03:00.360
was

00:03:00.360 --> 00:03:03.270
going on, and

00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:05.470
I wasn't expecting

00:03:05.480 --> 00:03:07.910
this at all.

00:03:07.920 --> 00:03:10.110
All of a

00:03:10.120 --> 00:03:12.750
sudden, I was in my garage and an angel

00:03:12.760 --> 00:03:14.670
came before me. I was interceding

00:03:14.680 --> 00:03:17.630
for a certain minister because

00:03:17.640 --> 00:03:20.149
the Lord had put me on an assignment.

00:03:20.159 --> 00:03:24.190
This angel comes to me in a vision.

00:03:24.190 --> 00:03:24.200
I'm

00:03:24.200 --> 00:03:25.789
not

00:03:25.799 --> 00:03:27.910
saying I'm able to touch this angel

00:03:27.920 --> 00:03:30.190
like physically flesh, but I'm able to see

00:03:30.200 --> 00:03:32.309
it in the spirit realm. It was

00:03:32.319 --> 00:03:35.750
dressed

00:03:35.760 --> 00:03:39.030
similarly

00:03:39.040 --> 00:03:41.990
to how Gabriel is

00:03:41.990 --> 00:03:42.000
dressed—very much

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:47.830
like a messenger.

00:03:57.200 --> 00:03:59.670
Warrior angels are really muscular

00:03:59.680 --> 00:04:01.270
and have armor on,

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:04.670
but these angels have robes and gowns and are

00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:09.229
always

00:04:09.239 --> 00:04:12.550
really tall.

00:04:12.560 --> 00:04:14.309
They're tall and slender,

00:04:14.319 --> 00:04:16.710
not bulky.

00:04:18.519 --> 00:04:21.310
They

00:04:21.320 --> 00:04:24.629
look like beanpole

00:04:24.629 --> 00:04:24.639
people—really

00:04:24.639 --> 00:04:27.990
skinny

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:30.510
and tall.

00:04:35.360 --> 00:04:38.550
This

00:04:38.560 --> 00:04:40.469
angel came to me like that. They don't

00:04:40.479 --> 00:04:41.430
have a

00:04:41.440 --> 00:04:43.909
gender; I'm trying my

00:04:43.919 --> 00:04:46.749
best to describe it. The hair

00:04:46.759 --> 00:04:49.590
is always curlier,

00:04:49.600 --> 00:04:51.909
and they have

00:04:51.919 --> 00:04:53.830
a band

00:04:53.840 --> 00:04:55.590
around their head

00:04:59.759 --> 00:05:01.629
like olive branches.

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:04.469
He

00:05:08.310 --> 00:05:08.320
said

00:05:10.919 --> 00:05:12.990
to

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:16.749
me,

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:34.309
'I've come with a message for

00:05:34.319 --> 00:05:36.909
you. The Lord has told me

00:05:36.919 --> 00:05:39.150
that Deuteronomy

00:05:39.160 --> 00:05:43.230
28:10 was going to become real to

00:05:43.230 --> 00:05:43.240
you.'He

00:05:43.240 --> 00:05:46.070
said it was going

00:05:46.080 --> 00:05:49.469
to become

00:05:58.150 --> 00:05:58.160
Rhema

00:06:04.479 --> 00:06:06.430
to

00:06:13.070 --> 00:06:13.080
you.

00:06:20.560 --> 00:06:23.110
In these last days,

00:06:24.960 --> 00:06:27.749
that verse is

00:06:27.759 --> 00:06:31.029
going to come alive inside of you, and

00:06:31.039 --> 00:06:34.070
you are going to have an umbrella of

00:06:35.880 --> 00:06:39.550
protection—a

00:06:43.919 --> 00:06:48.189
hedge over you.

00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:55.629
He told me to cheer up

00:06:55.629 --> 00:06:55.639
and

00:06:55.639 --> 00:06:57.749
not

00:06:57.759 --> 00:07:00.150
be afraid.

00:07:06.680 --> 00:07:08.469
He said, 'The Lord has instructed me

00:07:08.479 --> 00:07:11.469
to tell you Deuteronomy is going

00:07:11.479 --> 00:07:14.270
to come alive inside of

00:07:14.280 --> 00:07:16.790
you.'He

00:07:16.800 --> 00:07:19.629
said a supernatural

00:07:19.639 --> 00:07:21.990
covering is over you, your

00:07:22.000 --> 00:07:24.150
children, and your wife. He told

00:07:24.150 --> 00:07:24.160
me to

00:07:24.160 --> 00:07:25.629
tell that other minister you're

00:07:25.639 --> 00:07:28.350
interceding for that

00:07:28.350 --> 00:07:28.360
the

00:07:28.360 --> 00:07:31.629
scripture in Deuteronomy

00:07:31.639 --> 00:07:33.869
is going to come alive on them

00:07:33.879 --> 00:07:35.670
for the occult and the

00:07:35.680 --> 00:07:37.869
persecution they're receiving.

00:07:37.879 --> 00:07:41.469
There's a

00:07:41.479 --> 00:07:44.469
supernatural push that's coming alive,

00:07:44.479 --> 00:07:47.390
like God was breathing on that

00:07:47.400 --> 00:07:50.629
verse even more concerning you.

00:08:00.840 --> 00:08:02.790
It's going to be a

00:08:02.800 --> 00:08:05.749
hedge around you.

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:10.950
I just started

00:08:10.960 --> 00:08:12.550
worshiping the Lord. I

00:08:12.550 --> 00:08:12.560
needed

00:08:12.560 --> 00:08:14.110
that

00:08:14.120 --> 00:08:16.110
word.

00:08:20.230 --> 00:08:20.240
When

00:08:21.759 --> 00:08:23.510
the storm's going on

00:08:23.520 --> 00:08:25.430
around you,

00:08:25.440 --> 00:08:28.790
you don't whine

00:08:28.790 --> 00:08:28.800
or

00:08:28.800 --> 00:08:31.230
be

00:08:31.230 --> 00:08:31.240
mealy-mouthed

00:08:31.240 --> 00:08:32.870
because out of the abundance

00:08:32.880 --> 00:08:35.110
of the heart, the mouth speaks.

00:08:37.039 --> 00:08:38.709
If you think

00:08:38.709 --> 00:08:38.719
like

00:08:38.719 --> 00:08:41.070
a victim,

00:08:41.080 --> 00:08:43.509
the devil comes to

00:08:43.519 --> 00:08:45.670
try to kill, steal, and destroy. He

00:08:45.670 --> 00:08:45.680
is like

00:08:45.680 --> 00:08:47.550
a roaring lion seeking whom

00:08:47.560 --> 00:08:49.710
he may devour. He's coming to try to put

00:08:49.720 --> 00:08:51.630
out that flame

00:08:51.630 --> 00:08:51.640
because

00:08:51.640 --> 00:08:55.190
he doesn't like fire.

00:09:03.680 --> 00:09:06.710
Every

00:09:06.720 --> 00:09:08.829
time I

00:09:08.829 --> 00:09:08.839
go

00:09:08.839 --> 00:09:09.829
through something, the Lord says,

00:09:10.959 --> 00:09:14.030
'Remember your training, soldier.

00:09:14.040 --> 00:09:16.550
Remember to stand upright. Don't

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:18.829
let the enemy knock you down.

00:09:18.839 --> 00:09:21.190
You've got to

00:09:21.200 --> 00:09:23.750
get that Word down inside of

00:09:23.760 --> 00:09:26.230
you.'You

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:30.350
can pray all you want, but it is the

00:09:30.360 --> 00:09:33.829
Word that defeats the devil.

00:09:33.829 --> 00:09:33.839
James

00:09:33.839 --> 00:09:37.350
says

00:09:37.350 --> 00:09:37.360
to

00:09:37.360 --> 00:09:39.829
submit yourself therefore

00:09:39.839 --> 00:09:42.470
unto God, resist the devil, and he will

00:09:42.480 --> 00:09:45.150
flee from you. But you've got to submit.

00:09:45.160 --> 00:09:47.230
You've got to get that Word down inside

00:09:47.240 --> 00:09:50.550
of your spirit; that is your sword. It

00:09:50.560 --> 00:09:52.790
comes out of your mouth and

00:09:52.790 --> 00:09:52.800
is

00:09:52.800 --> 00:09:55.069
able to cut the devil up.

00:09:57.320 --> 00:09:59.670
Praying is

00:10:04.519 --> 00:10:06.030
communication with the

00:10:06.040 --> 00:10:09.069
Father and maneuvering the angels, but there are times

00:10:09.079 --> 00:10:10.509
when you're dealing with the demonic where you

00:10:10.509 --> 00:10:10.519
must be

00:10:10.519 --> 00:10:13.470
binding, loosing, and

00:10:13.480 --> 00:10:15.750
pleading the blood.

00:10:20.880 --> 00:10:23.990
The Word of the

00:10:24.000 --> 00:10:26.829
Lord is what gives you power in the

00:10:26.839 --> 00:10:29.150
spiritual realm.

00:10:33.240 --> 00:10:36.750
When Jesus was baptized in the

00:10:36.760 --> 00:10:39.990
River Jordan,

00:10:42.959 --> 00:10:44.509
the Holy Spirit ascended on Him like a

00:10:44.519 --> 00:10:46.910
dove, and a voice out of heaven spoke:

00:10:48.839 --> 00:10:50.750
'This is my Son,

00:10:50.750 --> 00:10:50.760
in

00:10:50.760 --> 00:10:54.350
whom I am well

00:10:56.790 --> 00:10:56.800
pleased.'I'm

00:10:59.440 --> 00:11:01.629
sure Lucifer heard

00:11:01.639 --> 00:11:03.550
it.

00:11:06.350 --> 00:11:06.360
Then

00:11:07.839 --> 00:11:11.030
the devil comes

00:11:11.030 --> 00:11:11.040
when

00:11:11.040 --> 00:11:13.670
Jesus is being tempted for forty days

00:11:13.670 --> 00:11:13.680
and

00:11:13.680 --> 00:11:16.389
tries to talk to

00:11:16.399 --> 00:11:18.509
Him: 'If you are the Son of

00:11:18.509 --> 00:11:18.519
God...'He

00:11:18.519 --> 00:11:21.550
started questioning it.

00:11:21.560 --> 00:11:23.430
He's a flesh devil;

00:11:23.430 --> 00:11:23.440
he

00:11:23.440 --> 00:11:25.550
doesn't

00:11:25.560 --> 00:11:27.550
think right. He

00:11:27.560 --> 00:11:29.670
has Alzheimer's or something.

00:11:33.040 --> 00:11:34.949
Jesus

00:11:37.560 --> 00:11:38.870
didn't

00:11:40.880 --> 00:11:44.389
combat him with

00:11:44.399 --> 00:11:46.389
natural things; He combated him

00:11:46.399 --> 00:11:48.710
with the Word. He

00:11:48.720 --> 00:11:52.990
said, 'It is

00:11:53.000 --> 00:11:55.110
written,

00:11:55.120 --> 00:11:57.670
Satan, tempt not the Lord thy

00:11:57.680 --> 00:11:59.509
God.'Every

00:11:59.519 --> 00:12:03.470
time He spoke back to

00:12:03.480 --> 00:12:06.629
the devil, He

00:12:10.800 --> 00:12:13.470
quoted scripture.

00:12:13.470 --> 00:12:13.480
He

00:12:13.480 --> 00:12:16.310
told

00:12:16.320 --> 00:12:18.629
the devil,

00:12:36.240 --> 00:12:38.590
'Get thee behind me,

00:12:38.590 --> 00:12:38.600
Satan.'That's

00:12:38.600 --> 00:12:40.269
what you have to do.

00:12:40.269 --> 00:12:40.279
Every

00:12:42.269 --> 00:12:42.279
time

00:12:42.279 --> 00:12:45.389
I

00:12:45.399 --> 00:12:47.509
deal with

00:12:51.310 --> 00:12:51.320
manifestations

00:12:55.320 --> 00:12:59.069
of

00:13:04.110 --> 00:13:04.120
critters

00:13:08.880 --> 00:13:11.389
trying

00:13:20.199 --> 00:13:24.550
to come against

00:13:24.550 --> 00:13:24.560
me,

00:13:24.560 --> 00:13:25.829
I've

00:13:25.829 --> 00:13:25.839
noticed

00:13:25.839 --> 00:13:27.189
that

00:13:27.199 --> 00:13:29.350
worship ticks them

00:13:29.360 --> 00:13:31.189
off. You can make them shut up

00:13:31.199 --> 00:13:33.030
when you start worshiping. I

00:13:33.040 --> 00:13:34.430
start praising the Lord, and

00:13:42.079 --> 00:13:44.230
they get out of

00:13:44.240 --> 00:13:48.189
here.

00:14:01.470 --> 00:14:01.480
I

00:14:16.279 --> 00:14:19.110
start quoting scripture,

00:14:22.269 --> 00:14:22.279
and

00:14:24.480 --> 00:14:26.670
the devil will flee from

00:14:26.670 --> 00:14:26.680
you

00:14:26.680 --> 00:14:29.990
in terror.

00:14:40.880 --> 00:14:43.030
The Lord

00:14:43.040 --> 00:14:45.189
has

00:14:45.199 --> 00:14:47.310
done everything He's going to do about

00:14:47.320 --> 00:14:51.710
the devil for you.

00:15:00.639 --> 00:15:02.590
Ephesians says we're seated with

00:15:02.600 --> 00:15:04.350
Him in the heavenlies, far above all

00:15:04.360 --> 00:15:06.470
principalities and powers.

00:15:08.680 --> 00:15:10.310
We take dominion and authority.

00:15:15.680 --> 00:15:17.590
You use

00:15:17.600 --> 00:15:18.949
Deuteronomy;

00:15:21.920 --> 00:15:23.710
that verse

00:15:41.959 --> 00:15:45.189
is for every believer.

00:15:45.199 --> 00:15:47.509
The

00:16:16.759 --> 00:16:19.749
devil

00:16:19.749 --> 00:16:19.759
recognizes

00:16:19.759 --> 00:16:22.670
authority just like a policeman

00:16:22.680 --> 00:16:24.910
standing at a traffic

00:16:24.920 --> 00:16:27.550
sign holding up his badge.

00:16:29.440 --> 00:16:32.509
By

00:16:32.519 --> 00:16:35.110
himself,

00:16:36.680 --> 00:16:38.710
he's just another average

00:16:38.720 --> 00:16:41.670
Joe, but he has the

00:16:41.670 --> 00:16:41.680
city and state

00:16:41.680 --> 00:16:43.670
backing him. He has that badge,

00:16:45.279 --> 00:16:47.670
and you obey

00:16:47.680 --> 00:16:50.629
because you recognize the authority.

00:16:50.639 --> 00:16:53.670
The devil recognizes if you

00:16:53.680 --> 00:16:56.230
know your authority

00:16:56.240 --> 00:16:58.629
in Christ and

00:17:00.639 --> 00:17:03.870
have that badge of the Holy Ghost. The

00:17:03.870 --> 00:17:03.880
blood of

00:17:03.880 --> 00:17:05.350
Jesus is

00:17:05.350 --> 00:17:05.360
your

00:17:05.360 --> 00:17:07.150
badge.

00:17:07.160 --> 00:17:09.069
You say, 'The blood of

00:17:09.079 --> 00:17:11.350
Jesus is against you, devil. You can't

00:17:11.360 --> 00:17:13.510
touch my house or my

00:17:13.520 --> 00:17:15.750
children.

00:17:22.839 --> 00:17:25.270
I command you to let my

00:17:25.280 --> 00:17:28.110
finances go right now!'I am a joint-heir with Jesus Christ, and I tell you, 'Thus far and no further!'I hold the blood—that's my

00:17:28.110 --> 00:17:28.120
badge—and

00:17:28.120 --> 00:17:31.470
I hold the blood of Jesus over this.

00:17:41.430 --> 00:17:41.440
If

00:17:53.640 --> 00:17:56.710
you start doing

00:17:56.720 --> 00:17:58.390
that, the devil's going to

